headline: 5 Monster Stocks to Hold for the Next 10 Years
summary: TSMC is set to benefit from the continued growth in AI infrastructure and semiconductors in general.  Pinterest is harnessing the power of AI to better monetize its large user base.  Dutch Bros has one of the best expansion stories in the restaurant space.
